Package com.warzone.team08.VM.map_editor.services

  • Class Summary
    Class Description
    ContinentService
    This service handles `editcontinent` user command to add and/or remove continent from the map.
    ContinentServiceTest
    This class tests the add and remove operations on continent.
    CountryNeighborService
    This service handles `editneighbor` user command to set/remove neighbors of the different countries on the map.
    CountryNeighborServiceTest
    This class tests the add and remove operations of neighbours of the country.
    CountryService
    This service handles `editcountry` user command to add/or remove country from the map.
    CountryServiceTest
    This class tests the add and remove operations on country.
    EditMapService
    This file loads map file in the user console.
    EditMapServiceTest
    This Class tests the blank fields available in the map file.
    LoadMapService
    This file loads map file in the user console.
    LoadMapServiceTest
    This Class tests the blank fields available in the map file.
    SaveMapService
    This class is to save the edited Map File.
    SaveMapServiceTest
    This file tests whether the map file is save successfully or not.
    ShowMapService
    This class is used to show the content of current map on user console
    ShowMapServiceTest
    This test class tests the ShowMapService class functions
    ValidateMapService
    This class contains methods for the validation of the map and handles `validatemap` user command.
    ValidateMapServiceTest
    This class tests ValidateMapService class for different types of validation requires for Map.
